# thoth_pam_settings

Manages PAM step-up enablement and outbound request/callback credentials.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_pam_settings" "pam" {
  pam_enabled                 = true
  pam_provider                = "okta"
  pam_callback_secret         = var.pam_callback_secret
  pam_request_url             = var.pam_request_url
  pam_request_secret          = var.pam_request_secret
  pam_request_auth_token      = var.pam_request_auth_token
  pam_request_timeout_seconds = 5
}
```
